| **Invited team member** | +25 | None |
| **Hit usage limit** | +20 | -10 per month |
| **Exported data** | +10 | -5 per month |
| **Connected integration** | +15 | None |
| **Daily active for 5+ days** | +20 | -10 per 2 weeks inactive |
""" ] ;
